StreamMessageRequest test: packet
=========================================================================

--- PD (Input):
packet {
  payload: "1"
  metadata {
    egress_port: "eth-1/2/3"
    submit_to_ingress: "0x1"
  }
}

--- IR:
packet {
  payload: "1"
  metadata {
    name: "egress_port"
    value {
      str: "eth-1/2/3"
    }
  }
  metadata {
    name: "submit_to_ingress"
    value {
      hex_str: "0x1"
    }
  }
}

